{"data":[{"id":561870338,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"8b2ec185053fbd9ffefeb740817ca938","url_token":"li-he-hao-75","name":"雷克雅未克的雪","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/a80218e956dbe2894c5376eeae51a07f_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/a80218e956dbe2894c5376eeae51a07f_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/8b2ec185053fbd9ffefeb740817ca938","user_type":"people","headline":"学生","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561870338","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546009439,"updated_time":1546009439,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":3,"comment_count":0,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e  关于这个问题， 我不能像其他答主一样嘲讽题主，因为，曾经的我也这么干过，人不中二枉少年嘛。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  初中的时候，有一段时间，疯狂的想找出素数分布的规律，也许像题主一样，沉浸在自己的所谓的激情中，确实很爽。但我能力有限，不像答主一样证明了哥猜，我最终什么都没有发现。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  后来，我听说，我们班主任，也是我们的数学老师，再跟其他班同学上课时，总会提到我，遗憾的说，我们班的那谁谁谁，要是把对数学的热情用在正确的方向，本身是可以很优秀的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  幸运的是，我没有像答主一样，把自己的前途，寄托在这些根本不可能实现的东西上，而是迷途知返，最后当然是通过考试而不是什么研究。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  我想说一句话，也是我们班主任告诉我的。一个非常业余的人研究一些非常专业的问题，除了浪费时间还有什么用呢？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  通过题主老师的答案，可以看出，题主是喜欢数学的，想证明哥猜想法也是很好的，Wiles不也是在10岁时就被费马大定理吸引住了，并从此选择了数学作为终身职业。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  可是，他也没有像你一样在没有系统的学习过数学前就去做这些工作啊。在他开始证明费马大定理前，已经是普林斯顿大学的教授了啊！并且在他决定向费马大定理发动冲击前，他先用18个月的时间，收集了这次战斗所必要的数学工具。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  接下来要做的，是长达10年的专心致志的努力。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  你还是高中生，不要想那么虚无缥缈的事情，如果你真的喜欢数学，那至少要考上大学后，掌握了足够的数学工具，才有可能实现你的梦想啊，虽然我觉得没戏。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  我觉得你要做的，就是把你所谓的证明撕了，烧了，扔了，总之忘了他，全身心投入高考中，想证明自己优秀，至少先拿下高考。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  你的问题在于读书太少，想的太多……总想好高骛远，结果眼前的都看不到。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"关于这个问题， 我不能像其他答主一样嘲讽题主，因为，曾经的我也这么干过，人不中二枉少年嘛。 初中的时候，有一段时间，疯狂的想找出素数分布的规律，也许像题主一样，沉浸在自己的所谓的激情中，确实很爽。但我能力有限，不像答主一样证明了哥猜，我最终…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=336\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Cedi